$MidnightBSD: src/contrib/mksh/MIDNIGHTBSD-upgrade,v 1.2 2009/11/26 15:44:25 laffer1 Exp $

Directions for updating OpenNTPD

1) Obtain the latest sources from OpenBSD FTP
2) Unpack sources.
3) Port to MidnightBSD.  (portable version no longer available)
4) Perform a test import of unpatched sources
 (change version number as needed)
cvs -q -n import -m "Import OpenNTPD 4.4" src/contrib/openntpd OPENNTPD v4_4

5) if all goes well, 
cvs import -m "Import OpenNTPD 4.4" src/contrib/openntpd OPENNTPD v4_4

6) Commit local changes to non vendor branch
7) update the Makefile and config files as necessary
